131
00:08:12,870 --> 00:08:17,050
Besides me, that lad Zeff is the only
one who uses that kitchen knife.

132
00:08:17,050 --> 00:08:21,270
"Lad"?! That damn geezer used
to be the captain of a pirate group!

133
