in order to go to the All Blue.

137
00:08:38,700 --> 00:08:40,490
All Blue, you said?

138
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:45,490
Yeah, a legendary sea that's said to
have the world's best foodstuffs...

139
00:08:45,490 --> 00:08:46,380
It's a miracle sea.

140
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:49,840
