161
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:04,330
Well, wait, lad.

162
00:10:04,330 --> 00:10:07,580
As thanks for the booze,
eat my food before you go.

163
00:10:07,580 --> 00:10:09,120
Oh, don't worry about it.

164
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,250
I wanna eat it!

165
