Hey, he's cutting them in a way
that makes use of his shaking hand.

180
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:30,870
Hm? He's adept for a drunk person.

181
00:11:41,260 --> 00:11:42,610
Here you go!

182
00:11:42,610 --> 00:11:43,630
Yaay!

183
