213
00:13:48,880 --> 00:13:49,590
Other stuff, huh?

214
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:52,440
Since Water Seven is a city of trade,

215
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:56,060
our store has all sorts of condiments
from around the world, so...

216
00:13:56,700 --> 00:14:01,020
